  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936100/extras/37cc4c6b77f2794264b167e3cd71a44e.avif?t=1643377184\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br><br>Master of Typing is a fun typing competition in which all depends on how fast you can type English texts. The most important skills you need here are high typing speed and good accuracy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936100/extras/f55698758cc18a2dd9af21797f3c7659.poster.avif?t=1643377184\" width=600 height=54 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936100/extras/f55698758cc18a2dd9af21797f3c7659.webm?t=1643377184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936100/extras/f55698758cc18a2dd9af21797f3c7659.mp4?t=1643377184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What's inside:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Lots of English texts to type and 10 difficulty levels.<br></li><li>10 skilled rivals to beat. You will need two things to complete all levels - high typing speed and accuracy.<br></li><li>Multicolored keyboard to learn the correct finger position while typing.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936100/extras/561e87467d4c0481adcdb191a3c06f51.poster.avif?t=1643377184\" width=600 height=54 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936100/extras/561e87467d4c0481adcdb191a3c06f51.webm?t=1643377184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936100/extras/561e87467d4c0481adcdb191a3c06f51.mp4?t=1643377184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Master of Typing combines not only fun, but also practice.<br>Playing Master of Typing you can learn to type fast without watching the keyboard. If you ever wanted to learn touch typing to enhance your productivity while working on a computer with English texts, this is the perfect app for you to apply this typing technique.<br><br>Master your typing speed to a great extent and get ready to show off your typing skills!",
